<div id='begin' class='container'>

	<div class='row'>

		<div class='span8 offset2'>

			<div class='hero-unit'>
				<h1>CommandMap Instructions</h1>
			</div>

			<% if flash[:notice] %>
			    <div id="notice" class="alert alert-error"><%= flash[:notice] %></div>
			<% end %>

			<div class='row'>
				<div class='span8'>
					<p>Like in the previous round, you will be presented with an icon and its name. </p>
					<p><strong>This time, you must hit CTRL to activate the menu. </strong> Your task remains the same. Find the icon and <span class='text-info'> click on it</span></strong>. If you click on an incorrect icon you will hear a beep sound.
					</p>
					<p>You must try to complete the task as fast and accurately as possible. <strong><span class='text-info'>A bonus will be given to the fastest and most accurate</span></strong>.</p>
					
					<a href="/intermediate" class='btn btn-primary btn-large'> Begin</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</div>